overview:
Victorian Plumbing is the UK’s largest bathroom retailer with large quantity of quality products.Find your ideal bathroom suite online now. When you’ve chosen your new bathroom, we promise to deliver it on the date we’ve agreed with you, so you know exactly where you are. Everything in our store is kept in stock at our warehouse, so you don’t have to wait to get your dream bathroom. We have developed great delivery service options to give you the maximum convenience and fastest possible delivery of your dream bathroom.

Victorian Plumbing specialises in supplying high quality bathrooms and showers at huge discounts. The company deals with high quality products and everything sold is covered by a full warranty.. Victorian Plumbing offer a staggering choice of top quality bathroom suites, shower enclosures, kitchen sinks, bathroom taps, central heating products etc. at internet only prices. Most available for fast delivery anywhere in the UK.
